            <h6 class="mt-4"><strong>CRUD Implementation</strong></h6>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Create:</strong> Users can add new parking reservations and save favorites.</li>
                <li><strong>Read:</strong> Users can view available spots, their reservations, and favorites.</li>
                <li><strong>Update:</strong> Users can modify reservations (e.g., time, duration).</li>
                <li><strong>Delete:</strong> Users can cancel reservations or remove favorites.</li>
            </ul>

